recipe.label: Northwest Passage Pizza (Curry Brandade Pizza)
ingredientLines: 1 1/2 cups warm water, between 100 and 115 degrees F, as measured with a candy thermometer (any hotter will kill the yeast - an organic leavener, too cool and the yeast won't be activated)
4 cups all-purpose flour, plus some extra for the dough board
6 medium potatoes (about 2 1/2 to 3 pounds), peeled, boiled, drained well, and mashed with
2 tablespoons butter (you want these potatoes to be "tight" mashed potatoes - not loose)
1 medium red onion, shaved thin with a mandoline
